QuestData.Title: Cages For All Occasions
QuestData.Description:
Okay, do not lose focus. I can feel Renathal's presence. It is faint but I can sense he is outside of the tower, at least.
Come, let's find him and get out of here.
QuestData.RewardText: I recognize you. Azeroth has been very busy lately, and her champions have been very much at the forefront of events. We must talk as soon as time allows.
